==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Applicant
<hw>Ap"pli*cant</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>applicans</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>applicare</ets>. See
<er>Apply</er>.]</ety> <def>One who apples for something; one who makes
request; a petitioner.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>applicant</qex> for a cup of water.</q>
<rj><qau>Plumtre.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The court require the <qex>applicant</qex> to appear in
person.</q> <rj><qau>Z. Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Applicate</ent>⟦br⟧
